<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.4">
<l>niṟaiyiṉāṟ kuṟaivillā neṭumpaṇaittōṇ maṭappiṉṉai</l>
<l>poṟaiyiṉāṉ mulaiyaṇaivāṉ poruviṭaiyē ḻaṭarttukanta</l>
<l>kaṟaiyiṉār tuvaruṭukkai kaṭaiyāviṟ kaḻikōlkai</l>
<l>caṟaiyiṉār kavarāta taḷirniṟattāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except the want for [our] fullness</l>
<l>we have no want for [our] sprout colour that is not seized by the low man,</l>
<l>[his] hand with a stick for the cows with coral on the rim of [his] garment, the black one(?)</l>
<l>who rejoiced in killing seven bulls in fight in order to be close to the weighty breasts</l>
	<l>of youthful Piṉṉai with long bamboo shoulders.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
